{"tid":1252682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★風水大決戰！】「心經簡林」完成改善工程","createTime":"2019-06-23T06:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T20:15:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4792aa323b636a2ded55b281dcf33638a09c6a9c","tid":1252682,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2945448/org/64a560f4c23440118109442778a9491b.jpg/C1MC3qoukGMaraOmkiCD01fyN00qW5gWXTBXT10wV08?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2945448%2Forg%2F64a560f4c23440118109442778a9491b.jpg%2FC1MC3qoukGMaraOmkiCD01fyN00qW5gWXTBXT10wV08%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5edba6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已故國學大師饒宗頤墨寶、位於大嶼山的「心經簡林」早前因欠保養而現裂紋。旅遊事務署指，<span style=\"color: red;\">「心經簡林」最近已完成設置改善工程</span>，包括增設饒宗頤教授生平紀念牌、平面指示圖和休息座椅，並增設二維條碼方便旅客瀏覽經更新的網上導覽資料，以及修整通道和方向指示牌等，讓巿民和旅客參觀時可以更便捷舒適，並享受更豐富的旅遊體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/343710/%E5%BF%83%E7%B6%93%E7%B0%A1%E6%9E%97-%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B-%E8%A8%AD%E9%A5%92%E5%AE%97%E9%A0%A4%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B3%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E7%A2%91-%E4%BA%8C%E7%B6%AD%E7%A2%BC%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F343710%2F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E6%259E%2597-%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B-%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%25A5%2592%25E5%25AE%2597%25E9%25A0%25A4%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E7%25A2%2591-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%25B4%25B9&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=c22f73b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/3437